===========

de_bulguksa

for Counter Strike: Source

===========

Description

Bulguksa is one of the most famous temples in Korea. It was originally built in 528 during the Silla period, but has been burnt a few times since and restored. This map includes lots of trees and several custom models. Check the website for updates.

Author Nathaniel Laughlin

Email nlaughli@ucsc.edu

Released 7 Nov 05
Update 9 Nov 05 (Repacked tree models, textures)

Files
de_bulguksa.bsp (162,177,580)
de_bulguksa.nav (1,783,097)

Installation

Put both the bsp and nav files in /counter-strike source/cstrike/maps
